90337608&amp;issue=20200617\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1592390337608%26issue%3D20200617&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VHx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=4847e26a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1592390337608&amp;issue=20200617</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">原來11月走左 10000 億，走多 2000 億佢就收皮！！！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"dd9f435b0b98b82d349b104ffd05d0fd32855f0e","tid":2386950,"uid":389613,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:59:48.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">香港人用 BNO 係搬石頭砸中共春袋</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原來用 BNO 離開係 Trump 一早 set 左比中共既計時炸彈！我地更應該繼承 Trump 既精神，用 BNO 逼 Biden 同中共開戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">只要有大批香港人離開，會造成現時已經虛弱既經濟徹底崩潰，而中共強行鎖國則引來百國聯軍。</span><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本１：支共反制 BNO 會引致戰爭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[武俠小說] 因為 BNO 香港變成外交博奕戰場！Trump 偷偷地幫香港插左支定海神針迫 Biden 打柒中共！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2377934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2377934</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本２：支共比 BNO 走引致經濟崩潰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[神話故事] 中共經濟末日狂奔，BNO 就係大衛與歌利亞決戰粒石頭。港人出走成就 Trump 滅共偉業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2380593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2380593</a><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n不論你係撐 Trump 既手足、定係支持滅共既手足，今次 BNO Visa 係時候身體力行，用你對腳投票去支持 Trump 呢條滅共戰線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"red\"> 多你一個好多，少你一個唔掂！你既決定將會成為世界走向正義定係腐敗既關鍵因素！</span>"},{"pid":"dcd7e8317eb992bff83a918fa7b558c5016d5998","tid":2386950,"uid":326037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:59:50.